OL,3,CMoment of 'astonishing strength' as
OL,4,Cwoman addresses her mother's killer
OL,6,FAs the lawyers, journalists, family
OL,7,Fmembers and security staff took their
OL,8,Fseats in Plymouth crown court on
OL,9,FFriday morning, the atmosphere was at
OL,10,Fonce filled with extreme tension and
OL,11,Fimmense sadness.
OL,13,FThere was no jury present, and little
OL,14,Fjeopardy - Paul Butler had entered his
OL,15,Fguilty plea weeks ago, and a life
OL,16,Fsentence was inevitable - but the next
OL,17,Ffour hours would produce shock and
OL,18,Ftears from those in court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
