OL,3,CMoment of 'astonishing strength' as
OL,4,Cwoman addresses her mother's killer
OL,6,FUntil today, the story of Claire's
OL,7,Fabusive relationship with the former
OL,8,Fdoorman was fragmented and incomplete.
OL,10,FButler, dressed in a white long-
OL,11,Fsleeved t-shirt and jeans, sat in the
OL,12,Fdock with his head in his hands as the
OL,13,Ffull picture was revealed.
OL,15,FHe placed a tracking device on her
OL,16,Fcar. He once stood outside her place
OL,17,Fof work, staring into her office. He
OL,18,Fposted cryptic messages on Facebook,
OL,19,Fone reading: "Don't mess with the man
OL,20,Fwho has nothing to lose."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
