OL,3,CMoment of 'astonishing strength' as
OL,4,Cwoman addresses her mother's killer
OL,6,FAn IOPC investigation will examine how
OL,7,Fthe police handled Claire's
OL,8,Fcomplaints. In the meantime, the force
OL,9,Fsays it has made changes to its
OL,10,Fstalking and harassment procedures.
OL,12,FAs Friday's hearing continued, CCTV
OL,13,Ffootage was played on screens mounted
OL,14,Fhigh on either side of the courtroom.
OL,15,FIt showed Butler's movements before,
OL,16,Fduring and after the attack.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
