OL,4,Cwoman addresses her mother's killer
OL,6,FHe bought kitchen knives from
OL,7,FSainsbury's. He lay in wait for
OL,8,FClaire's partner - his apparent target
OL,9,F- who was out with his running group
OL,10,Faround Plymouth's waterfront.
OL,12,FThe moment of the attack itself, and
OL,13,Fthe details - 23 fierce stab wounds,
OL,14,Fsome of them puncturing Claire's
OL,15,Fribcage and torso - were almost too
OL,16,Fmuch to take in.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
