OL,6,FAs Mr Maxwell reached the end of his
OL,7,Fstatement, the two men locked eyes for
OL,8,Fjust a few seconds and stared at each
OL,9,Fother. It was an extraordinary moment
OL,10,Fin a day nobody present will ever
OL,11,Fforget.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
